title: Rex In Rome S13 Ep165 - Time Heals No Wounds

Rex In Rome S13 Ep165 - Time Heals No Wounds

Time Heals No Wounds - When a young labourer falls to his death at a building site, Inspector Rivera and Rex suspect foul play. They soon discover that he had been the toy boy of the rich widow who owns the site, until he had fallen in love with her daughter. Stars Ettore Bassi. 

From Italy, in Italian
